f deferasirox is used in combination with other potentially nephrotoxic agents (e.', 'Major', 'pharmacodynamic', NULL, 'https://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/81704/', '', 'Ascorbic acid, Vitamin A, Potassium Iodide, Acetylcysteine, Nandrolone, Golimumab, Ustekinumab, Antithymocyte immunoglobulin (rabbit), Tocilizumab, Secukinumab, Canakinumab, More', 'Hydroxocobalamin, Fomepizole, Ipecac, Nitrous acid, Dexrazoxane, Oxygen, Lanthanum carbonate, Difelikefalin, Deferoxamine, Levoleucovorin, Arginine, More', 1767369485);
